<br>
I believe you can find it in cities that have 'libraries'. These townes would be the gnome city, Freeport, or Erudin. You'll find that many of the other summoned weapons we get through the 20's are found in the libraries as well, though many are now somewhat useless until you get sword of runes.<br>
<br>
Get to the moon and get your focus item spells and summon elemental defender, these are quite nice, and I think you'll really enjoy the focus effects. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381929"> Naladini </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
