<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1220">everquest.allakhazam.com/...?item=1220</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Choker of Majdd <br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM <br>
AC: +4 Int: +5 <br>
Weight: 0.1 <br>
Classes: All Classes <br>
Races: All Races <br>
Inventory Slot: Neck <br>
Effect: See Invisible (permanent, worn)<br>
<br>
Comes in handy for seeing him while invis, and it still has decent INT stats for low/mid levels. Saves you from having to stop, rememorize and recast see invisible on yourself every half hour. I bought it for about 200pp, but I've seen them for 500pp and higher. Really useful and is worth the cost.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showMessageRange?topicID=24.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showPrevMessage?topicID=24.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showNextMessage?topicID=24.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic&index=37><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.threadControl?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagici